Whenever two or more egos come together, drama of one \
kind or another ensues. But even if you live totally alone, you \
still create your own drama. When you feel sorry for yourself, \
that's drama. When you feel guilty or anxious, that's drama. \
When you let the past or future obscure the present, you are \
creating time, psychological time \'97 the stuff out of which \
